# Haunted Hearse Console Quick Reference

Serial Monitor @ **115200 baud** (case-insensitive)

---

## Help & Status
- `?` or `HELP` â€” show all commands 
- `CFG` â€” print current settings + sensor states 
- `MAP` â€” print beam â†’ scene mapping 

---

## Timing / Settings
- `HOLD <ms>` â€” set FrankenLab hold duration 
  *Example:* `HOLD 7000` 
- `COOL <ms>` â€” set cooldown/lockout duration 
  *Example:* `COOL 20000` 
- `BRIGHT <0..15>` â€” set display brightness 
  *Example:* `BRIGHT 12` 

- `SDEB <ms>` â€” set beam debounce time (0â€“2000 ms) 
- `SREARM <ms>` â€” set beam re-arm time (0â€“600000 ms) 

---

## EEPROM Persistence
- `SAVE` â€” save settings to EEPROM 
- `LOAD` â€” load settings from EEPROM 

> ðŸ’¡ Settings auto-load after power cycle if valid.

---

## Forcing States & Scenes

### By code
- `STATE <code>` 
  - 0 = Standby 
  - 1 = FrankenLab 
  - 2 = MirrorRoom 
  - 10 = PhoneLoading 
  - 11 = IntroCue 
  - 12 = BloodRoom 
  - 13 = Graveyard 
  - 14 = FurRoom 
  - 15 = OrcaDino 
  - 16 = FrankenLab 
  - 17 = MirrorRoom 
  - 18 = ExitHole 

### By name
- `SCENE <name>` 
  Examples: 
  - `SCENE STANDBY` 
  - `SCENE BLOODROOM` 
  - `SCENE GRAVEYARD` 
  - `SCENE FURROOM` 
  - `SCENE FRANKENLAB` 
  - `SCENE MIRRORROOM` 
  - `SCENE EXITHOLE` 

Aliases also work: `INTRO`, `LAB`, `EXIT`, etc.

---

## Workflow Example
```text
CFG
HOLD 6000
BRIGHT 10
SAVE
SCENE FRANKENLAB
MAP
